### Create a new aquarium
POST http://localhost:3000/api/aquariums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cube 2",
  "aquarium_type_id": "57f90d24-ae6c-45ba-9a53-a8f36a3116b9",
  "description": "A small cube-shaped aquarium with LPS corals.",
  "volume": 40
}

###

### Get a single aquarium (replace {id} with actual aquarium ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/aquariums/50ab2303-9362-4278-8b1c-f05a2282ee31
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Update aquarium name (replace {id} with actual aquarium ID)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/aquariums/50ab2303-9362-4278-8b1c-f05a2282ee31
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Cube"
}

###

### Update multiple fields (replace {id} with actual aquarium ID)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/aquariums/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Renamed Cube",
  "description": "Updated description with more details",
  "volume": 50
}

###

### Update aquarium type (replace {id} and {aquarium_type_id} with actual IDs)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/aquariums/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "aquarium_type_id": "{aquarium_type_id}"
}

###

### Delete aquarium (replace {id} with actual aquarium ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/aquariums/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Error examples - Invalid UUID format
GET http://localhost:3000/api/aquariums/invalid-uuid
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Error examples - Aquarium not found
GET http://localhost:3000/api/aquariums/99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Error examples - PATCH with empty name
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/aquariums/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}

###

### Error examples - PATCH with no fields
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/aquariums/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Error examples - PATCH with invalid aquarium_type_id
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/aquariums/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
